        {
            "title": "麗莎·庫克就川普要罷免她的聯儲會理事職務起訴川普",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克提起訴訟，挑戰總統唐納德·川普撤銷她理事職務的做法，圍繞聯儲會獨立性掀起了歷史性的法律鬥爭。庫克被指涉及抵押貸款申請欺詐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據法庭記錄，庫克周四在華盛頓聯邦法院提起了訴訟。起訴書暫未立即發布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Lisa Cook Sues Trump Over His Move to Oust Her From Fed Board</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BA%97%E8%8E%8E-%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B%E5%B0%B1%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%A6%81%E7%BD%B7%E5%85%8D%E5%A5%B9%E7%9A%84%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-132421690.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-28 22:50:45",
