        {
            "title": "歐洲央行7月會議紀要顯示 官員認為通膨風險「總體平衡」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲央行7月會議紀要顯示，多數官員認為通膨風險「總體平衡」，他們對於消費價格的展望仍然適用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四公佈的會議摘要顯示，儘管提及進一步降息，但在已八次降息後將存款利率維持在2%被視為「穩健」做法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">會議紀要稱，「多數成員認為通膨前景面臨的風險總體平衡。會議指出，近期歐元區經濟數據展現的韌性已在6月預測基準情境中充分體現，且該預測已獲得廣泛驗證。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場普遍預期歐洲央行將在不到兩周後第二次維持借貸成本不變。經濟學家預測12月將再次降息，但投資者已不再充分消化進一步降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多數決策者認為當前利率水平合理，通膨率維持在2%目標附近，經濟迄今對關稅、戰爭等逆風因素展現出韌性。7月，歐盟與美國達成貿易協議，為該地區多數出口商品鎖定15%的關稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB Officials Saw Inflation Risks as ‘Broadly Balanced’ in July</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C7%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E7%B4%80%E8%A6%81%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA-%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%B8%BD%E9%AB%94%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1-133949423.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 01:15:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
