            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒　426瓶「酒王」估值超過呢個數｜財經熱話",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"楊受成首次拍賣美酒，426瓶瓶珍酩估值逾千萬。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Qv8TDFg.7XiOEPZU405p0Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/sl/am730_578/f98a5f0f1e7b2925e2efc216e7a3b241\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">楊受成首次拍賣美酒，426瓶瓶珍酩估值逾千萬。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>英皇國際(163)主席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:楊受成;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/楊受成\">楊受成</a>首次推出私人美酒窖藏拍賣。據香港蘇富比資料，「楊受成博士至尊窖藏珍酩」拍賣會將於9月10日下午3時舉行。今次拍賣</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>匯集楊受成窖藏中426瓶「至尊窖藏珍酩」，總估值高達逾千萬港元</span></span></span></span></span>，引發關注。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">涵蓋羅曼尼康帝等  「無一不是傳世經典」</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>根據</span><span>蘇富比網頁介紹，楊受成此次拍賣的美酒</span></span></span></span></span>涵蓋多款傳世名釀，<span><span><span><span><span>除了羅曼尼康帝(Romanée Conti)特級園系列外，還有Henri Jayer、Leroy、Coche-Dury、柏翠堡等名莊的珍釀，強調「其集中程度遠遠超越世界上任何倉存」。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>蘇富比洋酒部亞洲區主管更寫道，當</span></span></span></span></span>踏入<span><span><span><span><span>楊受成</span></span></span></span></span>酒窖時「為之震撼，<span><span><span><span><span>映入眼簾的皆是頂級瑰釀，整齊陳列着洋酒界中最偉大的名字」，並</span></span></span></span></span>讚譽「此處所藏，無一不是傳世經典。」</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">此前英皇傳出166億債務危機</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span>此前，英皇國際傳出債務危機，</span></span></span><span><span><span>6</span></span></span><span><span><span>月份公告顯示截至3月底逾期貸款達166億港元，<span><span>遭核數師「不發表意見」，其後傳出向債權人提交債務重組方案，尋求延長銀行貸款期限，惹來輿論關注。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒-426瓶-酒王-估值超過呢個數-財經熱話/593759?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒-426瓶-酒王-估值超過呢個數-財經熱話/593759?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒-426瓶-酒王-估值超過呢個數-財經熱話/593759?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A5%8A%E5%8F%97%E6%88%90%E7%A0%B4%E5%A4%A9%E8%8D%92%E6%8B%8D%E8%B3%A3%E8%97%8F%E9%85%92-426%E7%93%B6-%E9%85%92%E7%8E%8B-%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E6%95%B8-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-091500863.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-28 17:35:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
