        {
            "title": "看圖論市：南向資金淨賣出港股逾200億港元 創歷史最大",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zejrveX9zsM0ZzkG7rSHLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3cf578c29cfe1a7a5cd38f5e2446235b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oppV95wp2MF6Zio88fUC_A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/78057f42050bfb73bf5e9bacd4769e40\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 周四A股和港股再度呈現強弱分化走勢，內地南向資金在港股走弱之際大額淨賣出。彭博數據顯示，今日南向資金淨賣出港股逾204億港元，為紀錄最大單日淨賣出。恒生指數午後收窄部分跌幅，但收盤仍跌0.8%，而上證綜指則收升逾1.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9C%8B%E5%9C%96%E8%AB%96%E5%B8%82-%E5%8D%97%E5%90%91%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E6%B7%A8%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E9%80%BE200%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83-%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7-081750016.html",
